    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should call my doctor but the clinic is closed until monday and i'm literally in pain right now. i just need to know if it's actually dangerous or if people take it all the time. like is it just a 'better safe than sorry' thing or is there a real risk to the baby?",
